com.vector.cfg.util.scripting.dynamic

Interface IDynamicObjectAware

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IApplicationScriptExecutionContext, IDomainApi, IProject, IProjectScriptExecutionContext, IScriptCreationApi, IScriptCreationApi.IScriptExecutionContextWithNotExecutableReasons, IScriptCreationApiWithFields, IScriptExecutionContext

    @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
 @PublishedApiDomain(value=AUTOMATION_IF)
public interface IDynamicObjectAware
    A instance implementing IDynamicObjectAware marks itself that it has an underlying IDynamicObject, which could be enhanced at runtime.
